abstract: Anna Meares of Australia wins gold medal keirin at track cycling world championships in Saint-Quentin-En-Yvelines, France.
lead_paragraph: The sprinting star Anna Meares of Australia became the most successful female track cyclist in history, claiming her 11th world title.
